    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Personalization lets the view controller offer support for incorporating people",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "into the images it generates. When enabled, the view controller allows someone",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to build images that include:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A person from their Photos library",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "A character represented by an appearance and a skin tone",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When enabled, the view controller offers a way to import an image of",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a person from the Photos library. It also supports choosing someone",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "from a people picker, and by detecting names in any input text and using",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "that information to find images.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The default value of this property is ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ImagePlayground/documentation/ImagePlayground/ImagePlaygroundPersonalizationPolicy/automatic",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ",",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "which corresponds to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.ImagePlayground/documentation/ImagePlayground/ImagePlaygroundPersonalizationPolicy/enabled",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
